### Get a fresh admin token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "carol@clicknback.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Pass"
}

### Get a fresh token for testing (regular user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@clicknback.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Pass"
}

### Happy path: list all purchases — no filters (200 OK)
# Should return a paginated list of all seed purchases (>= 6 rows in seeds/all.sql)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Happy path: filter by status=confirmed (200 OK)
# Should return only the confirmed purchase (txn_seed_005)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases?status=confirmed
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Happy path: filter by status=reversed (200 OK)
# Should return only the reversed purchases (txn_seed_006)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases?status=reversed
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Happy path: filter by user_id — alice (200 OK)
# Should return only purchases belonging to alice
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases?user_id=b7e2c1a2-4f3a-4e2b-9c1a-8d2e3f4b5c6d
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Happy path: filter by merchant_id — Shoply (200 OK)
# Should return only purchases at Shoply
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases?merchant_id=a1b2c3d4-e5f6-4a7b-8c9d-0e1f2a3b4c5d
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Happy path: filter by date range (200 OK)
# Should return purchases created in the past 7 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases?start_date=2026-03-02&end_date=2026-03-09
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Happy path: pagination — page 2, page_size 2 (200 OK)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases?page=2&page_size=2
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Happy path: filter yields empty results (200 OK with empty items)
# Use an unknown user_id — no purchases match, total = 0
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases?user_id=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Sad path: unauthenticated request (401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases

### Sad path: non-admin user attempts access (401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases
Authorization: {{userToken}}

### Sad path: invalid page number (422 Unprocessable Entity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases?page=0
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### Sad path: invalid page_size — exceeds max (422 Unprocessable Entity)
GET {{baseUrl}}/purchases?page_size=200
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
